commit.message:
Also need these

Even though the code that uses the Teakra API can call the AHBM memory
access callbacks itself directly, AHBM also does some weird stuff on
misaligned accesses, for which these functions are probably useful.
Add 16- and 32-bit read/write interface to AHBM
expose some AHBM registers through the API
